FLEX is used to design the overall structure of a webpage
FLEXBOX will take full control over webpage and apply its rules to all the elements

sample code

 <style>
    p {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: inline-flex ;
    }

    li {
      list-style: none;
      display:  inline-flex;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: gold;
      display: inline-flex;
    }

  </style>
